Subject: Re: [VB] GL4 was: Parts stores

If you do use GL-5, use one that has a MT rating, then it is safe to use.
A GL-4 will still shift smoother than GL-5 will.
If you drive in very cold weather, synthetic GL-4 is another step better for
smoother shifting.

